        <p><strong>Windows NT 3.5</strong> is an <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Operating System', 'IT'); ?> developed by <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Microsoft', 'C'); ?>, released on 21 September 1994. It is the second release of <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Windows NT', 'WIS'); ?>.</p>
